title: Bikewatch
description: Visualization of BlueBike traffic in Boston and Cambridge.

title: Persuasive/Deceptive Visualization
description: Exploration of how design choices of a data visualization can impact the story it tells. The creation of two visualizations of data that argue for opposing sides of a proposition.

title: Visualization Critique and Redesign
description: Conducting a deep analysis and critique of an existing visualization and using the takeaways to design new visualizations that address issues in the original visualization while keeping its strengths.

title: Exploratory Data Analysis
description: Exploration of a dataset surrounding residential zoning laws in Greater Boston Municipalities to fomulate questions. Manipulating the data to get the story it tells, answer questions, and formulate new questions.
